{{zh-forms|alt=𥘅,𡭕,𱍐,視-“to show”}}

===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p|5}} – an altar. The original form is similar to unrelated character {{lang|zh|[[丅]]}}, and additional strokes are added to prevent confusion with an ancient variant of [[下]] and the ancient version of [[主]]. See also [[帝]]. Unrelated to [[小]] and the bottom part of [[京]].

